As part of https://github.com/ember-cli/ember-cli/pull/10734 you can see that we're proposing to publish a bunch of packages under the `@ember/*` prefix: 

```
@ember/classic-addon-blueprint 6.7.0-alpha.2 (patch)
@ember/classic-app-blueprint 6.7.0-alpha.2 (patch)
@ember/blueprint-blueprint 0.0.1 (patch)
@ember/blueprint-model 0.0.1 (patch)
```

After discussions amongst the team we're a little nervous adding new modules to the `@ember/` namespace so we discussed moving them to `@ember-tooling/` 👍

